          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets consisted of thin layers 0.5 to 4 mg/cm**2",
                "of various light elements deposited on thick gold",
                "backing discs. The oxygen target was prepared by",
                "smearing a suspension of analytically pure lead dioxide",
                "in distilled water on to the gold backing. A lead",
                "peroxide target of thickness 0.15 MeV, deposited",
                "on a thick gold backing was used. The carbon target was",
                "prepared by collecting soot on a gold backing disc from",
                "the burning of camphor. The thickness of the layer was",
                "estimated to correspond to an energy loss of 30 kev.",
                "The sulphur target was prepared in a similar manner by",
                "subliming the sulphur on to a gold backing. Its",
                "thickness was estimated to correspond to an energy loss",
                "of 100 keV."
              ]
            }
          ],
